Source: skytools3
Section: database
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Dimitri Fontaine <dim@tapoueh.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), autotools-dev, autoconf (>= 2.65), libevent-dev, python-all-dev, python-support, python-psycopg2, xmlto, asciidoc, libpq-dev, postgresql-server-dev-8.4, postgresql-server-dev-9.0
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://wiki.postgresql.org/wiki/Skytools
Vcs-Git: http://github.com/markokr/skytools.git
